v1.4 12/21/99
These are TSDIS HDF/hdf manipulation programs.

The programs are:

    print_vdata  -- Print all metadata information, stored as vdata,
                    to stdout.

    modify_vdata -- Modify any field and value with in a vdata.
                    This is an inplace modification.

    modify_all_hdf.pl  -- Run 'modify_vdata' on all hdf|HDF (.gz|.Z) files
                          in the current directory.  Command line arguments
                          are exactly those for 'modify_vdata'.

Installation:

    configure
    make install

Requirements:

    HDF 4.1*


Questions:

  help@trmm.gsfc.nasa.gov





